<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<meta content="initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=2.0, user-scalable=no, width=device-width" name="viewport">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
		<title>隔空传</title>
		<link href="__HOME_CSS__/mui.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
		<style>
			* {
				padding: 0;
				margin: 0;
			}
			
			body {
				background-color: #eee;
			}
			
			.top {
				width: 100%;
				height: 50%;
				background-color: #fff;
				padding-top: 4rem;
			}
			
			.top-img {
				margin: 0 auto;
				width: 12.5rem;
				height: 10rem;
				background-color: #fff;
			}
			
			.top-img>img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			
			.text {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 0.65rem;
				width: 15rem;
				height: 2.5rem;
				margin: 0 auto;
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				background-color: #fff;
				line-height: 1rem;
			}
			
			.txt {
				background-color: #fff;
				width: 100%;
				height: 2.5rem;
			}
			
			.int {
				width: 100%;
				height: 2rem;
				margin-top: 0.75rem;
				line-height: 2rem;
				position: relative;
			}
			
			.int>input {
				border: none;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				font-size: 0.6rem;
				padding-left: 2.5rem;
			}
			
			.spin {
				width: 100%;
				height: 2.5rem;
				line-height: 3rem;
				padding-left: 0.75rem;
				font-size: 0.5rem;
				color:#d24242;
			}
			
			.spins{
				width: 100%;
				height: 3rem;
				padding-left: 0.75rem;
				font-size: 0.5rem;
				color:#d24242;
			}
			.int-img {
				display: block;
				width: 1rem;
				height: 1.5rem;
				position: absolute;
				top: 0.6rem;
				left: 1rem;
			}
			
			.int-img>img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			
			.max {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				background-color: #eee;
			}
			.send>input{
				width: 100%;
				height: 3rem;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				background-color: #2AB7CF;
				text-align: center;
				color: #fff;
				line-height: 2rem;
				border:none;
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<div class="top">
			<div class="top-img">
				<img src="__HOME_IMAGES__/frimessage_top.png" alt="" />
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="txt">
			<div class="text">输入好友手机号，点击发送，您的V网将以短信传送给您的好友</div>
		</div>
		<div class="int"><i class="int-img"><img src="__HOME_IMAGES__/frimessage_left.png" alt="" /></i><input type="text" class="phone" placeholder="输入接收手机号，将名片付给Ta" /></div>
		<div class="spin">*每天最多隔空传10次</div>
		<div class="spins">*如果发送成功，对方未接收到；请您去更改V网姓名再次发送。</div>
		<div class="send"><input type="submit" value="发 送"/></div>
		<input type="hidden" class="user_id" value="{$user_info['id']}">
		<input type="hidden" class="openid" value="{$openid}">
		<script src="__HOME_JS__/rem.js"></script>
		<script src="__HOME_JS__/jquery.js"></script>
		<script src="__HOME_JS__/mui.min.js"></script>

		<script>
         $(".send").click(function () {
             var phone = $('.phone').val();
             var user_id = $('.user_id').val();
             var openid = $('.openid').val();
             var _url = "{:U('Home/User/frimessage')}";
             $.post(_url,{"user_id":user_id,"mobile":phone,"openid":openid},function(res){
                 // console.log(res);return;
                 if(res.code==1){
                     mui.toast(res.msg);
                 }else{
                     mui.toast(res.msg);
                     setTimeout(function(){
                         top.location.href="{:U('Home/User/frimessage')}";
                     },1000);
                 }
             });

         })
		</script>
		<script src="http://res.wx.qq.com/open/js/jweixin-1.0.0.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript">
			document.addEventListener('WeixinJSBridgeReady', function onBridgeReady() {
				// 通过下面这个API隐藏右上角按钮hideOptionMenu
				WeixinJSBridge.call('hideOptionMenu');
			});
		</script>
	</body>


</html>